5823b7e1debdc3189f037e9474e1214b24d75a37.query:
(SELECT DISTINCT dp.hash as "hash!" FROM document_parts dp
        INNER JOIN documents d ON d.id = dp.document_id AND d.bulletin_id = $1)
       UNION
       (SELECT DISTINCT hash as "hash!" FROM pubkeys WHERE bulletin_id = $1)
       UNION
       (SELECT DISTINCT signature_hash as "hash!" FROM pubkeys WHERE bulletin_id = $1)
       UNION
       (SELECT DISTINCT signature_hash as "hash!" FROM document_part_signatures WHERE bulletin_id = $1)

       UNION
       (SELECT DISTINCT hash as "hash!" FROM story_snapshots WHERE bulletin_id = $1)
       UNION
       (SELECT DISTINCT evidence_hash as "hash!" FROM pubkey_domain_endorsements WHERE bulletin_id = $1)
       UNION
       (SELECT DISTINCT evidence_hash as "hash!" FROM email_addresses WHERE bulletin_id = $1)
       UNION
       (SELECT DISTINCT hash as "hash!" FROM terms_acceptances WHERE bulletin_id = $1)

       ORDER BY "hash!"

7ce390f521c5089ab21528d10ab1cffd80cee3ff.query:
SELECT id as "id!: i32", 
subscription_id as "subscription_id!: Option < i32 >", 
stripe_customer_id as "stripe_customer_id!: Option < String >", 
public_name as "public_name!: Option < String >", 
logo_url as "logo_url!: Option < String >", 
deletion_id as "deletion_id!: Option < i32 >", 
created_at as "created_at!: UtcDateTime", 
web_callbacks_url as "web_callbacks_url!: Option < String >" FROM orgs WHERE id IN (
      SELECT d.org_id FROM documents d
      INNER JOIN email_addresses ea ON d.org_id = ea.org_id
      LEFT JOIN parked_reminders pr ON d.org_id = pr.org_id
      WHERE d.bulletin_id IS NULL
        AND NOT d.funded
        AND d.created_at < ($1::TIMESTAMPTZ - INTERVAL '2 DAYS')
        AND (pr.created_at IS NULL OR pr.created_at < ($1::TIMESTAMPTZ - INTERVAL '30 DAYS'))
      GROUP BY d.org_id)

      INNER JOIN terms_acceptances ta ON d.org_id = ta.org_id
      AND ta.accepted IS NOT NULL AND NOT d.funded

subscription_id as "subscription_id!: Option < i32 >", 
stripe_customer_id as "stripe_customer_id!: Option < String >", 
public_name as "public_name!: Option < String >", 
logo_url as "logo_url!: Option < String >", 
deletion_id as "deletion_id!: Option < i32 >", 
created_at as "created_at!: UtcDateTime", 
web_callbacks_url as "web_callbacks_url!: Option < String >" FROM orgs WHERE id IN (
      SELECT d.org_id FROM documents d
      INNER JOIN terms_acceptances ta ON d.org_id = ta.org_id
      AND ta.accepted IS NOT NULL AND NOT d.funded
      GROUP BY d.org_id
    )
    ORDER BY (SELECT SUM(cost) FROM documents WHERE NOT funded AND org_id = orgs.id)
    DESC LIMIT $1 OFFSET $2
